Filters
Let's get back to the post list for a minute. It offers sorting and pagination, but one feature is missing: the ability to search content.
Admin-on-rest can use input components to create a multi-criteria search engine in the list view. First, create a  component just like you would write a  component, using input components as children. Then, add it to the list using the filters prop:
